WEBVTT

00:00:27.838 --> 00:00:30.220
do ritma otkucaja srca,

00:00:30.220 --> 00:00:33.742
utičući tako na sve i jednu ćeliju.

00:00:34.884 --> 00:00:37.523
Endokrini sistem se oslanja
na interakciju tri elementa

00:00:37.523 --> 00:00:39.692
kako bi obavio svoj posao:

00:00:39.692 --> 00:00:40.615
žlezda,

00:00:40.615 --> 00:00:41.520
hormona,

00:00:41.520 --> 00:00:44.294
i biliona ćelijskih receptora.

00:00:44.294 --> 00:00:47.444
Prvo, postoji više žlezda koje
proizvode hormone:

00:00:47.444 --> 00:00:48.815
3 u mozgu,

00:00:48.815 --> 00:00:51.161
i 7 u ostatku tela.

00:00:51.161 --> 00:00:54.033
Svaka je okružena mrežom krvnih sudova,

00:00:54.033 --> 00:00:58.452
odakle crpe sastojke putem kojih
stvaraju desetine hormona.

00:00:58.452 --> 00:01:01.736
Ovi hormoni se onda u malim
količinama ispumpavaju,